#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Micrometer"
msgstr "Micrômetro"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The https://quarkus.io/guides/telemetry-micrometer[Micrometer Quarkus extension] provides metrics from automatic instrumentation implemented in Quarkus and its extensions."
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/guides/telemetry-micrometer[A extensão Micrometer Quarkus] fornece métricas provenientes da instrumentação automática implementada no Quarkus e em suas extensões."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "There are multiple ways to output Micrometer metrics. Next there are some examples:"
msgstr "Existem várias maneiras de exibir métricas do Micrometer. A seguir, apresentamos alguns exemplos:"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using the Micrometer Prometheus registry"
msgstr "Utilização do registro Micrometer Prometheus"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is the most common way to output metrics from Micrometer and the default way in Quarkus. The Micrometer Prometheus registry will publish data in the `/q/metrics` endpoint and a scraper inside the Grafana LGTM Dev Service will grab it (*pull* data from the service)."
msgstr "Essa é a forma mais comum de gerar métricas a partir do Micrometer e a forma padrão no Quarkus. O registro do Micrometer no Prometheus publicará os dados no endpoint `/q/metrics` , e um scraper dentro do Grafana LGTM Dev Service irá obtê-los ( *extrair* os dados do serviço)."

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using the Micrometer OTLP registry"
msgstr "Utilização do registro Micrometer OTLP"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The https://docs.quarkiverse.io/quarkus-micrometer-registry/dev/micrometer-registry-otlp.html[Quarkiverse Micrometer OTLP registry] will output data using the OpenTelemetry OTLP protocol to the Grafana LGTM Dev Service. This will *push* data out of the service:"
msgstr "link:https://docs.quarkiverse.io/quarkus-micrometer-registry/dev/micrometer-registry-otlp.html[O registro OTLP do Quarkiverse Micrometer] enviará dados, utilizando o protocolo OTLP do OpenTelemetry, para o Grafana LGTM Dev Service. Isso fará com que os dados *sejam enviados* a partir do serviço:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When using the https://micrometer.io/[Micrometer's] Quarkiverse OTLP registry to push metrics to Grafana OTel LGTM, the `quarkus.micrometer.export.otlp.url` property is automatically set to OTel collector endpoint as seen from the outside of the Docker container."
msgstr "Ao utilizar o registro Quarkiverse OTLP link:https://micrometer.io/[do Micrometer] para enviar métricas ao Grafana OTel LGTM, a propriedade ``quarkus.micrometer.export.otlp.url` ` é definida automaticamente como o endpoint do coletor OTel, conforme visto de fora do contêiner Docker."

#. type: Title ==
