#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus.otel.exporter.otlp.endpoint` property is automatically set to the OTel collector endpoint as seen from the outside of the Docker container."
msgstr "A propriedade ` `quarkus.otel.exporter.otlp.endpoint` ` é definida automaticamente como o endpoint do coletor OTel, conforme visto de fora do contêiner do Docker."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
